description:
Go to http://hellofresh.com/mlm16 and use code mlm16 to get 16 free meals plus 3 free gifts.

Go to http://mintmobile.com/mlm to cut your wireless bill to $15 a month.

Go to http://upstart.com/mlm to find out how Upstart can lower your monthly payments.

Juicero created a 400 dollar machine to make juice with packets you could squeeze out…by hand. Some of these companies just make us question why anyone thought this would be a good idea to begin with.

Welcome to Multi Level Mondays, a weekly series all about multi level marketing, pyramid schemes, and ponzi schemes.
